Author: davidw
Content: I wonder how things like this might affect startups coming out of universities.  In the past, there were people like Dr. Ousterhout who, realizing they had something hot on their hands, would spin it out into a company from the University.  A large corporation breathing down your neck might crimp that to some degree.
